title: Are there two songs that aren't released?
subtitle: The rumors are that the Beatles recorded the songs "The Curious Rings" and "The Paper T-shirt in Pink Letmos," which are still not released until today.
author: David Mikkelson
vclaim: The Beatles record songs are entitled "Colding Circles," "Left Right (and Wrong)," "Pink Letmos Papershirt," and "Dick Chair," all still unreleased to this day.
